text: Stitzer is an unincorporated community in the town of Liberty in Grant County, Wisconsin, United States.Stitzer, Wisconsin ==History== A post office called Stitzer has been in operation since 1879. The community was named for Bernard Stizer, a local farmer. ==Notes== Category:Unincorporated communities in Grant County, Wisconsin Category:Unincorporated communities in Wisconsin
title: Stitzer, Wisconsin
